snippet.title: My Candy Love - University Life: Trailer
snippet.description:
▼▼▼ Contest information below! ▼▼▼

Ready for a new adventure? Incarnate a young student in her final year at university, meet the colorful characters and different personalities! Who knows? You may find love...

Discover My Candy Love - University Life!

To celebrate the upcoming release of the game, participate in the Thumbs Up contest! ♥
Are you up for a challenge? If the trailer video obtains enough “Likes” on YouTube before June 6th, an exclusive gift will be offered at the release of the game. We’ll tell you more when the video has received 5,000 likes on YouTube! We are counting on you ;)

More information: https://www.facebook.com/mycandyloveofficial/
My Candy Love: https://www.mycandylove.com/
